dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Map shows Afghanistan/Pakistan province-level, and Pakistan agency, district, or frontier region boundaries, federal administered tribal areas, 1972 line of control. Includes location map. "98 pk 12-09 State (INR)." North-West Frontier Province was changed to Khyber Pakhtunkhwa in 2010.
